snippet.title: Baladins - Official Cinematic Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the announcement trailer for Baladins, an upcoming choose-your-own-story multiplayer game (1-4 players online) inspired by Role-Playing Games. 

A whole campaign with friends, packed in 1-hour sessions.
